Package com.ezasm.assembler

Interface Argument

All Known Subinterfaces:
Argument.Immediate
All Known Implementing Classes:
Argument.Dereference, Argument.Immediate.Character, Argument.Immediate.Integer, Argument.Immediate.String, Argument.Label, Argument.Register
public sealed interface Argument permits Argument.Register, Argument.Dereference, Argument.Label, Argument.Immediate
An algebraic datatype used to store instruction dispatch arguments. These are used by Assembler and are used as the arguments to InstructionDispatcher.execute(ArrayList).
